# {{mcu}} Architecture Knowledge

## Overview

- **Core**: ARM {{core}} (ARMv7E-M)
- **FPU**: No (Soft-float required)
- **Clock**: Up to 72 MHz (System), 36 MHz (Bus)
- **Flash**: 128 KB
- **SRAM**: 32 KB (16 KB SRAM_L + 16 KB SRAM_U)

## Memory Map

| Region | Start | End | Size | Description |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| Flash | `0x0000_0000` | `0x0001_FFFF` | 128 KB | Program Code & Constants |
| SRAM_L | `0x1FFF_C000` | `0x1FFF_FFFF` | 16 KB | Lower SRAM (Code/Data) |
| SRAM_U | `0x2000_0000` | `0x2000_3FFF` | 16 KB | Upper SRAM (Data/Stack) |
| Peripherals | `0x4000_0000` | `0x400F_FFFF` | 1 MB | AIPS-Lite Peripheral Bridge |
| Private Periph | `0xE000_0000` | `0xE00F_FFFF` | 1 MB | NVIC, SysTick, SCB |

## Interrupt Vector Table

Located at `0x0000_0000` (Flash start). Relocatable to SRAM via VTOR (`0xE000ED08`).

| IRQ | Source | Description |
|---|---|---|
| - | Reset | Initial PC and SP |
| - | NMI | Non-Maskable Interrupt |
| - | HardFault | All fault conditions |
| 0-15 | DMA0-15 | DMA transfer complete |
| 31 | ADC0 | ADC0 conversion complete |
| 32 | ADC1 | ADC1 conversion complete |
| 33 | FTM0 | FlexTimer 0 |
| 34 | FTM1 | FlexTimer 1 |
| 44 | UART0 | UART0 Status/Error |
| 45 | UART1 | UART1 Status/Error |

## System Constraints

- **Stack Size**: 0x1000 (4KB) recommended (Check `.ld` file for exact value)
- **Heap**: Minimal or zero (Avoid `malloc` in critical paths)
- **Endianness**: Little-endian
- **Alignment**:
    - 4-byte alignment for 32-bit access
    - Instructions must be half-word aligned

## Boot Sequence

1. Hardware Reset
2. Fetch MSP from `0x0000_0000`
3. Fetch PC from `0x0000_0004` (Reset_Handler)
4. `SystemInit()` (Clock setup, WDT disable)
5. `__libc_init_array()` (C++ constructors/static init)
6. `main()`

